1. On je čuo njegovog* psa u dvorištu. (He heard his dog in the yard.)
2. Njegovog* sina je upoznao u školi. (He met his son in school.)
3. Svi smo čuli njegovog* govora. (We all heard his speech.)
4. Njegovog* brata je videla kako se sprema za put. (She saw his brother preparing for the trip.)
5. Često je posmatrala njegovog* psa u parku. (She often watched his dog in the park.)